97 provision of quality health and long-term care services to all enrollees regardless of physical or
98 mental health conditions.
99 (n) PACE programs shall meet all privacy standards set by the regulations established by
100 the federal Department of Health and Human Services under the Healthcare Insurance Portability
101 and Accountability Act of 1996.
102 (o) MassHealth shall promulgate regulations to enforce the provisions of this chapter.
